    <h1>Littering</h1>
        <img src="/Italylitter.png" alt="Littering" class="smaller-image">
      <p> it's crucial to be aware of and respect the local rules and regulations that contribute to the preservation of its cultural heritage and public spaces. The country's commitment to maintaining its historical sites and picturesque landscapes extends to everyday behaviors. For instance, there are strict rules against littering, sitting, eating, or drinking near churches, public buildings, and in public spaces. These measures aim to ensure that these significant sites remain clean, well-preserved, and respectful environments for everyone. Obedience to posted signs and guidelines is not only a legal requirement but also a mark of courtesy to the local community and the nation's rich history. </p>
